sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as KServe Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant RBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant API as vLLM API Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP (localhost)
    participant Worker as HPUWorker<br/>(in-process)
    participant Gaudi as Intel Gaudi Device<br/>SynapseAI HAL
    participant S3 as S3/MinIO Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HF as Hugging Face Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,Gaudi: Flow 1: Model Inference Request
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (JWT)<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Gateway->>RBAC: Forward request<br/>HTTPS/8443<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    RBAC->>API: Forward (localhost)<br/>HTTP/8000<br/>No auth (trusted)
    API->>Worker: Dispatch inference<br/>(in-process call)
    Worker->>Gaudi: Execute model forward<br/>SynapseAI HAL
    Gaudi-->>Worker: Inference result
    Worker-->>API: Response tensor
    API-->>RBAC: JSON response
    RBAC-->>Gateway: HTTPS response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON prediction result

    Note over Client,Gaudi: Flow 2: Model Loading at Startup
    API->>S3: Download model weights<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>AWS IAM / Access Key
    S3-->>API: Model artifacts
    API->>HF: Download tokenizer/config<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer Token (optional)
    HF-->>API: Tokenizer + config files
    API->>Worker: Load model to HPU
    Worker->>Gaudi: Transfer weights to device memory

    Note over Worker,Gaudi: Flow 3: Multi-Card Tensor Parallelism (HCCL)
    participant Worker_N as HPUWorker rank N<br/>(peer card)
    Worker->>Worker_N: HCCL all-reduce<br/>Dynamic port<br/>Plaintext (in-cluster)
    Worker_N-->>Worker: Collective result
    Note right of Worker: Tensor/pipeline parallelism<br/>via HCCL protocol

    Note over Worker,Gaudi: Flow 4: KV Cache Disaggregation (NIXL)
    participant Decode as Decode Instance<br/>HPU memory
    Worker->>Decode: KV cache transfer<br/>NIXL side channel (HTTP)<br/>Plaintext, no auth
    Worker->>Decode: Direct memory transfer<br/>NIXL / RDMA<br/>No encryption
    Note right of Worker: Block size conversion +<br/>NHD/HND layout transform<br/>for heterogeneous configs
